asset.hookText:
Char-Broil LIVE from The Weather Channel - May 4, 2013 7:40am 

Char-Broil All-Star Chef Christo Gonzales - grilling up chicken fajitas on a Char-Broil TRU-Infrared grill for Cinco de Mayo on The Weather Channel in Atlanta, GA at TWC headquarters. You can find the recipe for this dish along with any others featured on The Weather Channel over at http://live.charbroil.com/twc 

During May and June watch The Weather Channel Saturday mornings at :40 past the hour from 7:40am to 10:40am for grilling tips and recipes from Char-Broil All-Stars. Bookmark the URL above and check back every Saturday for the latest recipe used in the program.

If you want to find out more about Char-Broil TRU-Infrared, please visit http://live.charbroil.com/what-is-tru-infrared
